We have implemented a Brain Computer Interface (BCI) for image reconstruction based on Rapid Serial Visual Presentations (RSPVs) of polygons, that act as primitives for images.
An LDA classifier was trained to discriminate brain activity and retrieve correct pieces from given pictures.
